Feature: manage_recipes
  A collaborator can create a recipe
  And its ingridients
  Then can tagged if the tag does not exist
  A collabotor can request to create a new tag
  And send to evaluate to admin in order to be published

  Scenario: I should be able to create a new recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to create ingridients

  Scenario: I should be able to tag a recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to edit a recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to delete a recipe
